<item>
            <title>[LU-5385] HSM: do not call the JSON log functions if no log is open</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5385</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;llapi_hsm_log_ct_registration() and llapi_hsm_log_ct_progress() are&lt;br/&gt;
very expensive (fid2path+allocations). Do not let them do anything &lt;br/&gt;
if llapi_hsm_write_json_event() is going to discard the JSON record.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This impacts the performance of the copytool.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
